# AI Promptbook v2

Native desktop app (React 19 + TypeScript + Tauri 2 / Rust) for managing AI agent instruction files, system prompts, and project templates.

## Architecture
- `src/features/` – one folder per page/route
- `src/ui/` – shared components and layout
- `src/services/` – all Tauri IPC calls
- `src/state/` – Zustand global stores
- `src/domain/` – pure types and utilities
- `src-tauri/src/lib.rs` – Rust Tauri commands

## Rules
- Functional React components + hooks only; no `any` in TypeScript
- File I/O via `@tauri-apps/plugin-fs`; never browser storage APIs
- GitHub tokens must always be encrypted; use `src/services/cryptoService.ts`
- Rust commands return `Result<T, String>`; fix all `clippy` warnings
- Run `tsc --noEmit` to validate TypeScript before finishing
